OL,3,CHillsborough probe finds 12 officers
OL,4,Cwould have faced gross misconduct cases
OL,6,F"Fundamental failures" and "concerted
OL,7,Fefforts" to pin the blame on Liverpool
OL,8,Ffans during the Hillsborough disaster
OL,9,Fwould have resulted in gross
OL,10,Fmisconduct proceedings, an
OL,11,Finvestigation has found.
OL,13,FA new report published by the
OL,14,FIndependent Office for Police Conduct
OL,15,F(IOPC) has found that 12 officers
OL,16,Fwould have faced misconduct
OL,17,Fproceedings under current laws.
