OL,3,CHillsborough probe finds 12 officers
OL,4,Cwould have faced gross misconduct cases
OL,6,FHowever, the IOPC says that
OL,7,Fproceedings cannot be brought because
OL,8,Flegislation at the time of the
OL,9,Finvestigation prevented officers from
OL,10,Fbeing disciplined after they retire.
OL,12,F97 Liverpool supporters died at the FA
OL,13,FCup semi-final on 15 April 1989 when
OL,14,Fpolice opened an exit gate to the
OL,15,Fground to alleviate crowding outside
OL,16,Fand failed to direct supporters away
OL,17,Ffrom the tunnel leading to the central
OL,18,Fpens where the crush happened.
