OL,3,CHillsborough probe finds 12 officers
OL,4,Cwould have faced gross misconduct cases
OL,6,FIOPC deputy director general Kathie
OL,7,FCashell said the victims, their
OL,8,Ffamilies and survivors had been
OL,9,F"repeatedly let down".
OL,11,FShe said: "First by the deep
OL,12,Fcomplacency of South Yorkshire Police
OL,13,Fin its preparation for the match,
OL,14,Ffollowed by its fundamental failure to
OL,15,Fgrip the disaster as it unfolded, and
OL,16,Fthen through the force's concerted
OL,17,Fefforts to deflect the blame onto the
OL,18,FLiverpool supporters, which caused
OL,19,Fenormous distress to bereaved families
OL,20,Fand survivors for nearly four decades.
