OL,6,F"They were let down again by the
OL,7,Finexplicably narrow investigation into
OL,8,Fthe disaster conducted by West
OL,9,FMidlands Police, which was a missed
OL,10,Fopportunity to bring these failings to
OL,11,Flight much sooner."
OL,13,FNicola Brook, a solicitor at Broudie
OL,14,FJackson Canter acting for several
OL,15,Fbereaved families, said it was a
OL,16,F"bitter injustice" that no-one would
OL,17,Fbe held to account.
