OL,6,FShe said: "This outcome may vindicate
OL,7,Fthe bereaved families and survivors
OL,8,Fwho have fought for decades to expose
OL,9,Fthe truth ` but it delivers no justice.
OL,11,F"Instead, it exposes a system that has
OL,12,Fallowed officers to simply walk away,
OL,13,Fretiring without scrutiny, sanction or
OL,14,Fconsequence for failing to meet the
OL,15,Fstandards the public has every right
OL,16,Fto expect.
OL,18,F"Yes, the law has now changed so this
OL,19,Floophole cannot be used in future. But
OL,20,Ffor those affected by this case, that
OL,21,Fis no consolation.
