OL,6,F"They are left with yet another bitter
OL,7,Finjustice: the truth finally
OL,8,Facknowledged, but accountability
OL,9,Fdenied."
OL,11,FAmong those who would have had cases
OL,12,Fto answer for gross misconduct were
OL,13,FSouth Yorkshire Police's then-chief
OL,14,Fconstable Peter Wright and match
OL,15,Fcommander David Duckenfield, as well
OL,16,Fas Sir Norman Bettison, who went on to
OL,17,Fbecome chief constable of Merseyside
OL,18,FPolice.
