OL,6,FThe IOPC and Operation Resolve
OL,7,Finvestigations into the tragedy and
OL,8,Fits aftermath were launched in 2012,
OL,9,Ffollowing the Hillsborough Independent
OL,10,FPanel report.
OL,12,FThe West Midlands officers who led the
OL,13,Finvestigation into the disaster,
OL,14,FMervyn Jones, who was assistant chief
OL,15,Fconstable, and then-detective chief
OL,16,Fsuperintendent Michael Foster, were
OL,17,Freferred to the CPS for their failings
OL,18,Fbut the threshold for prosecution was
OL,19,Fnot found to have been met, according
OL,20,Fto the report.
