OL,3,CHillsborough probe finds 12 officers
OL,4,Cwould have faced gross misconduct cases
OL,6,FThe IOPC said both former officers
OL,7,Fwould have a case to answer for gross
OL,8,Fmisconduct after failing to conduct a
OL,9,Frigorous investigation because they
OL,10,Fwere "biased towards the force and
OL,11,Fagainst the supporters".
OL,13,FMr Duckenfield, 81, a chief
OL,14,Fsuperintendent on the day, was cleared
OL,15,Fof gross negligence manslaughter by a
OL,16,Fjury in 2019.
