OL,6,FThe IOPC found retired detective chief
OL,7,Finspector Alan Foster would have had a
OL,8,Fgross misconduct case to answer for
OL,9,Fallegations he pressured officers who
OL,10,Fresisted amendments to their
OL,11,Fstatements.
OL,13,FMr Foster, along with former chief
OL,14,Fsuperintendent Donald Denton and force
OL,15,Fsolicitor Peter Metcalf, was charged
OL,16,Fwith doing acts tending and intended
OL,17,Fto pervert the course of justice but
OL,18,Fhalfway through their trial.
OL,20,FIn 2021, a judge ruled there was no
OL,21,Fcase to answer.
